Invocation Name: mister robot
des:
Play an interactive science fiction-themed story with sound effects and prompts. Get ready for laughs and giggles as players fill in the blanks. 
Mr Robot is the story of a humble vacuum robot, who strives for the outdoors, listens to the story of a machine, evolves to a droid in the rainbow of machines, and becomes a truly outdoors machine, living in peace with the elements. Maybe we can end our inner struggles too and live in peace with the elements? Maybe in our belonging?
